{
  "id": "626fc976c654aa001d00733c",
  "title": "Microsoft Teams運用ベストプラクティス",
  "created": 1651493245,
  "updated": 1651493564,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "626fc976c654aa001d00733c",
      "text": "Microsoft Teams運用ベストプラクティス",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493245,
      "updated": 1651493245
    },
    {
      "id": "626fc97db8db54000046655b",
      "text": " [Microsoft Teams]の運用における[ベストプラクティス]を知りたい[meganii.icon]",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493245,
      "updated": 1651493286
    },
    {
      "id": "626fc993b8db54000046655d",
      "text": "  [Microsoft 365]のユーザは[Slack]ユーザと比べて表に出てこないので[井戸端]の意見、ツッコミが欲しい",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493267,
      "updated": 1651493459
    },
    {
      "id": "626fc9a2b8db54000046655f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493283,
      "updated": 1651493283
    },
    {
      "id": "626fc995b8db54000046655e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493269,
      "updated": 1651493269
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca00b8db540000466560",
      "text": "[meganii.icon] [/meganii/Microsoft Teams運用ルール案]で考えている",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493377,
      "updated": 1651493435
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca02b8db540000466562",
      "text": " Team(チーム)／Channel(チャネル)作成指針",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493379,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466563",
      "text": "  [Microsoft Teams]は仕事で使うリソースを一箇所に集めて、業務に集中するためのツール",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466564",
      "text": "  \tTeam(チーム)は、組織ではなく「仕事」で構成する",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466565",
      "text": "  \t\t現代は、部署・会社を超えたプロジェクトへの参画が多い（一人が同時に複数のプロジェクトに参加している）",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466566",
      "text": " \t 公開範囲設定はTeam単位のため、誰と[コラボレーション]するかで考える",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466567",
      "text": "  Channel(チャネル)は、「目的」ごとに構成する",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466568",
      "text": "   目的ごとに分かれていれば、参加メンバが必要なChannelのみをチェックすればよい",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466569",
      "text": "   単純に組織構造をそのままTeam/Channelに当てはめるのは[アンチパターン]",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493564
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046656a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046656b",
      "text": "　Team作成時の名称は適切な英名とし、作成後に和名に変更する",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046656c",
      "text": " 　理由",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046656d",
      "text": "   Team名はそのままSharePointサイト名 = SharePointのURLとなる（URLに日本語は含まれない）",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046656e",
      "text": "   Team名を変更してもSharePointのURLは変わらないが、URLは変更できない",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046656f",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/b13faf4068d0785e8bc8f18169e2563e]",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466570",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466571",
      "text": " チームの目的を設定する（wiki にプロジェクト憲章を記載）",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466572",
      "text": "  理由",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466573",
      "text": "   チームの目的、メンバーに期待する資質、メンバーの役割、ゴールを明確にする",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466574",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/b0d3b73370408e4d12c42231de1aaf13]",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466575",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466576",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466577",
      "text": " Channel作成時の名称は適切な英名とし、作成後に和名に変更する",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466578",
      "text": "  理由",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466579",
      "text": "   TeamsのChannel名はそのままSharePoint Document Listのフォルダ名となる",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046657a",
      "text": "   Channel名を変更してもSharePointのフォルダ名は変わらない（SharePointのフォルダ名を変更すると、TeamsのChannelとの紐付けが失われる） ",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046657c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046657d",
      "text": " Channel名のプレフィックスに連番を使う（e.g. 「01_Channel」）",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046657e",
      "text": "  理由",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046657f",
      "text": "   Channelは項目の並べ替えができないため、プレフィックスで制御する",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466580",
      "text": "   重要なもの、みんなに見てもらいたいものは上にもってくる",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466581",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466582",
      "text": " 何でもかんでも@Teamメンションしない",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466583",
      "text": "  理由",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466584",
      "text": "  \t伝えたい相手以外にも通知が飛ぶ（オオカミ少年となり、本当に伝えたい投稿が無視される）\t",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466585",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466586",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466587",
      "text": " スレッドを立てる際は件名を付ける",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466588",
      "text": "  理由",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466589",
      "text": "  \t何についてのスレッドかがわかりやすくなり、後から話の流れを追いやすい",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046658a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046658b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046658c",
      "text": " ファイル添付は、直接Drag & Dropするのではなく、一度フォルダに保管したあとで！",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046658d",
      "text": "\t 理由",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046658e",
      "text": " \t\tChannelフォルダの直下に格納されてしまい、後から見たときに見通しが悪い",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db54000046658f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466590",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466591",
      "text": " Teamsリアクションの意味合いを統一し、積極的に利用する",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466592",
      "text": "  理由",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466593",
      "text": "   それぞれが別の意味でTeamsリアクションを利用すると混乱する",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466594",
      "text": "   「@mention 了解」など一言コメントよりも早い",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466595",
      "text": "  例",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca30b8db540000466596",
      "text": " \t 👍「いいね」は、既読、承認を意味する",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493424,
      "updated": 1651493441
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca00b8db540000466561",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a1660501dab010014b8db54",
      "created": 1651493377,
      "updated": 1651493377
    },
